data.description: Nice porch front home in Cobbs Creek! Enter into a bright living room with wood floors, fireplace mantle and large window. Separate dining room with window and wood floors. Updated eat in kitchen with breakfast area, tile floor, cherry wood cabinets, gas stove, dishwasher, refrigerator, garbage disposal, pendant lighting, recessed lighting and door to nice sized yard. The basement is unfinished but great for storage, mechanicals (gas hot water tank, gas hot air heat w/central air, laundry sink, washer and dryer. On the second floor there is a spacious, bright front bedroom with three windows, closet and ceiling fan. Modern full tile bath with tub and skylight. Middle bedroom with closet and ceiling fan. Additional bedroom with ceiling fan. Large rear bedroom with ceiling fan, closet and two windows. This is a 4 bedroom, 1 bath home with wood floors, updated kitchen and bath. Schedule your showing today!
